         <ab>VVrS88.1 (mss. 4010, 4020, 4025, 4040, 4050, 4055, 4060, 4161, 4162):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>yaθā ahū vairiiō</em> čahār guftan zōhr abar māhrōy barsom nihādan ud pad harw yatāhuwairyō frāztar burdan ō ī sar ī barsom</ab> 
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "He should recite four <em>yaθā ahū vairiiō</em> and put the <em>zōhr</em> on the <em>māhrōy</em> and <em>barsom</em>. At each yatāhuwairyō, he should move it 
            further forward towards the end of the <em>barsom</em>."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
